name: Planet Pers
description:
A Space Traveler detected a massive anomaly ahead of her spaceship. It was a Blackhole. 
Unfortunately for her, there's nothing she can do to escape the massive gravity. 
Second later she got sucked in and when she regain consciousness, her spaceship was undamaged but running out of antimatter. She stranded in a beautiful lust planet that she called it "Planet Pers" Pers means purple in her language.
